## Description

Replaces boxing `ArrayList` with `List<SourceValueInfo>`, greatly improving performance and decreasing allocations on this kind of hot path. Also removes static field of composing `Array.Empty<SourceValueInfo>()` as it has no impact on storing it.

I've also removed the `bool isIndexer` as it just complicates the `switch` statement, added explicit accessibility modifiers, and sealed the class as it has no derivates.

